-consume-74-kilogrammes-of-raw-and-30-litres-of-water-it-easier-for-engineers-called-for-the-development-of-mobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F13080-manufacturing-phone-consume-74-kilogrammes-of-raw-and-30-litres-of-water-it-easier-for-engineers-called-for-the-development-of-mobile&d=tBA5YcuxkehEJyaRdq29iZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=78ca326e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/13080-manufacturing-phone-consume-74-kilogrammes-of-raw-and-30-litres-of-water-it-easier-for-engineers-called-for-the-development-of-mobile</a>"},{"pid":"4ad8530e788fd66c38ae4dc1b50c40a0fb5abea0","tid":967413,"uid":42513,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:31:35.000Z","msg":"其實d環保撚 千奇唔好有近視 因為鏡片係膠黎 大部分鏡框都係膠， 唔準擦牙 因為牙擦成隻都係膠， 到衣著，全部唔準著衫褲鞋襪底衫褲 因為d衫係有膠成份。<br />\n<br />\n同埋全部唔準用手提 因為電話又係有膠 就算全部電話俾你全金屬 你張sim卡都係膠。"},{"pid":"0075989c18667aba3edb19735e641237ac2d0e4e","tid":967413,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}